Construction 4.0 & Digital Twins Roadmap — Jordan
This repository supports Al‑Btoush et al. (2026) "Artificial Intelligence, Digital Twins and Education 4.0 in Jordan: A Phased, Expert‑Informed Roadmap". It contains PRISMA search exports, deduplication & screening logs, scripts for deduplication and inter‑rater reliability (Cohen’s kappa), PRISMA flow figure, KPI and feasibility templates, and analysis notebooks.

Repository structure

/prisma_and_search: raw exports, merged/dedup files, screening spreadsheets, scripts, PRISMA figure
/manuscript_assets: figures, KPI_register.xlsx, feasibility_template.xlsx
/code: analysis notebooks and scripts
